msgctxt "sn15.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Bhātusutta "
msgstr "16. Brother "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn15.16:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati … pe … "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.16:1.2"
msgid "“na so, bhikkhave, satto sulabharūpo yo nabhātābhūtapubbo … pe … "
msgstr "“It’s not easy to find a sentient being who in all this long time has not previously been your brother. … "

msgctxt "sn15.16:1.3"
msgid "alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. "
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.16:1.4"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

